description: Tens of thousands rallying in Minsk are met by a huge police turnout and dozens of arrests.
title: Belarus protest: Mass rally keeps pressure on Lukashenko
title_page: Belarus protest: Mass rally keeps pressure on Lukashenko - BBC News
maintext: Reporting at the height of the protests, the BBC's Steve Rosenberg in Minsk said there were far more police than on the past two Sundays when similar rallies were held. Some protesters lay down on the road to try to prevent riot police from moving, with others chanting "disgrace" and "go away".
